Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）\Nユールの支度は終わりそう？
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be done preparing for Yule?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yule?
