Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エリアス）ユール
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.52,0:02:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I call them the Yule twins because they\Nalways come on the day of the winter solstice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冬至の日に いつも やって来るから\Nユールの双子と呼んでいるけど
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't really know their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のことは分からない
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be busy today.
