Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, I promise.
