Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ルツ）俺は使い魔 失格だ
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure of a familiar.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help Chise when she's in trouble.
