Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,He's been like this ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセ）\Nこの間から こんな状態です
