Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エリアス）\N君は 僕より ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チセのことを\N分かってるんだろう
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be tough for you to say\Nanything because Chise tends to hide things,
