Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.99,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An ancient being, Ashen Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセ）\N古きもの 灰の目
Dialogue: 5,0:23:58.20,0:24:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Siblings that are at the mercy of his eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悠久の時を生きる彼に\N翻弄される姉弟(きょうだい)
Dialogue: 5,0:24:02.17,0:24:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The mage and the girl lend them a hand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法使いと少女は\N姉弟たちのために手を貸すが…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ステラ）返して！ 私の弟よ
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.88,0:24:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back! He's {\i1}my{\i0} brother!
